<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Environment Variables on Data Science | DSChloe</title><link>https://dschloe.github.io/tags/environment-variables/</link><description>Recent content in Environment Variables on Data Science | DSChloe</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 01:00:47 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://dschloe.github.io/tags/environment-variables/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>OS별 환경변수 설정 (Linux &amp; macOS / Windows)</title><link>https://dschloe.github.io/programming/2025/02/environment_variables/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Feb 2025 01:00:47 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://dschloe.github.io/programming/2025/02/environment_variables/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="1-linux--macos"&gt;1. &lt;strong&gt;Linux &amp;amp; macOS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="11-임시-환경변수-설정-현재-세션에서만-유효"&gt;1.1 &lt;strong&gt;임시 환경변수 설정 (현재 세션에서만 유효)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export 변수명&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;값
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;예)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export PATH&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;$PATH:/usr/local/bin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export JAVA_HOME&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk-17.jdk/Contents/Home
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;위 설정은 현재 터미널 세션에서만 유효하며, 터미널을 닫으면 사라진다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="12-영구-환경변수-설정"&gt;1.2 &lt;strong&gt;영구 환경변수 설정&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-bash-shell-bash-사용-시"&gt;(1) &lt;strong&gt;Bash Shell (bash 사용 시)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;~/.bashrc&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 또는 **&lt;code&gt;~/.bash_profile&lt;/code&gt;*에 추가&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export 변수명&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;값
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;예)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export PATH&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;$PATH:/usr/local/bin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export JAVA_HOME&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk-17.jdk/Contents/Home
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;적용:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;source ~/.bashrc &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# 또는 source ~/.bash_profile&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="2-zsh-shell-macos-기본-shell"&gt;(2) &lt;strong&gt;Zsh Shell (macOS 기본 Shell)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code&gt;~/.zshrc&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; 파일 수정:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export 변수명&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;값
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;예)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export PATH&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;$PATH:/usr/local/bin
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;export JAVA_HOME&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk-17.jdk/Contents/Home
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;적용:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>